<!-- ===== PHILOSOPHY ===== -->
<section class="section" id="philosophy">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="philosophy-layout">
      <div class="philosophy-header">
        <p class="section__eyebrow">Philosophy</p>
        <h2 class="section__title">Learning in the age of AI</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="philosophy-content">
        <blockquote class="pullquote">
          "The illiterate of the 21st century will not be those who cannot read and write, but those who cannot learn, unlearn, and relearn."
          <cite>— Alvin Toffler</cite>
        </blockquote>
        <p>The most consequential shift in knowledge work isn't that AI can answer questions — it's that the <strong>cost of learning has collapsed</strong>. What used to require a course, a mentor, or a decade of trial and error can now be explored in an afternoon with the right tools and the right questions.</p>
        <p>But speed without direction is just noise. Craig Claw exists because I believe the professionals who will thrive are those who build <strong>systems for compounding knowledge</strong> — not just consuming it.</p>
        <div class="philosophy-principles">
          <div class="principle">
            <span class="principle__number">01</span>
            <h3 class="principle__title">Curiosity as infrastructure</h3>
            <p class="principle__text">Every question you ask an AI is a seed. Build a system to plant them deliberately, track what grows, and prune what doesn't.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="principle">
            <span class="principle__number">02</span>
            <h3 class="principle__title">Depth over breadth</h3>
            <p class="principle__text">AI makes it trivially easy to skim a hundred topics. The edge comes from going deep — developing intuition that no model can replicate.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="principle">
            <span class="principle__number">03</span>
            <h3 class="principle__title">Output as proof of understanding</h3>
            <p class="principle__text">Writing, building, teaching — these are how you convert information into knowledge. AI accelerates the loop, but you still have to close it.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="principle">
            <span class="principle__number">04</span>
            <h3 class="principle__title">Compound daily</h3>
            <p class="principle__text">A 1% improvement in your system each day means you're 37x better in a year. The discipline of daily refinement is the real competitive advantage.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

